<h3 id="统计分析">统计分析</h3>
<h4 id="where-条件过滤">where 条件过滤</h4>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-Shell">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-Shell" data-lang="Shell"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># select * from table;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">awk <span class="m">1</span> table_file
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># select * from table where cost &gt; 100;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">awk <span class="s1">&#39;$2&gt;100&#39;</span> table_file</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h4 id="对某个字段去重或者按记录去重">对某个字段去重，或者按记录去重</h4>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-Shell">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
