    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-Shell" data-lang="Shell"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># select distinct(date) from table;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">awk <span class="s1">&#39;!a[$3]++{print $3}&#39;</span> table_file
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># select distinct(*) from table;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">awk <span class="s1">&#39;!a[$0]++&#39;</span> table_file</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h4 id="记录按序输出">记录按序输出</h4>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-Shell">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
