<h4 id="分组求和统计关键词group-byhavingsumcount">分组求和统计，关键词：group by、having、sum、count</h4>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-Shell">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-Shell" data-lang="Shell"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># select id, count(1), sum(cost) from table group by id having count(1) &gt; 2;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">awk <span class="s1">&#39;{a[$1]=a[$1]==&#34;&#34;?$2:a[$1]&#34;,&#34;$2}END{for(i in a){c=split(a[i],b,&#34;,&#34;);if(c&gt;2){sum=0;for(j in b){sum+=b[j]};print i&#34;\t&#34;c&#34;\t&#34;sum}}}&#39;</span> table_file</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h4 id="模糊查询">模糊查询</h4>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-Shell">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-Shell" data-lang="Shell"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># select name from table where name like &#39;wang%&#39;;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">awk <span class="s1">&#39;$2 ~/^wang/{print $2}&#39;</span> table_file
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># select addr from table where addr like &#39;%bei&#39;;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">awk <span class="s1">&#39;/.*bei$/{print $3}&#39;</span> table_file
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># select addr from table where addr like &#39;%bei%&#39;;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">awk <span class="s1">&#39;$3 ~/bei/{print $3}&#39;</span> table_file</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h4 id="多表-join-关联查询">多表 join 关联查询</h4>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-Shell">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-Shell" data-lang="Shell"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># select a._ , b._ from table a inner join table b on a.id = b.id and b.id = 2;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">awk <span class="s1">&#39;ARGIND==1{a[$1]=$0;next}{if(($1 in a)&amp;&amp;$1==2){print a[$1]&#34;\t&#34;$2&#34;\t&#34;$3}}&#39;</span> table_file table_file</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h4 id="多表-union-all">多表 union all</h4>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
